{"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":0,"metadata":{"colab":{"provenance":[],"authorship_tag":"ABX9TyPusamvdVdACoSWAtIUOHbM"},"kernelspec":{"name":"python3","display_name":"Python 3"},"language_info":{"name":"python"}},"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["# **Тема:** создание автономного агента, способного выполнять задачи, состоящие из нескольких шагов, работа с инструментами (tools) и планированием\n"],"metadata":{"id":"XuSeebT_idjh"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["**Задачи:**\n","\n","Разработка агента с помощью Smolagents\n","\n","1. Определить набор инструментов для простого агента (например, поиск в интернете, калькулятор, работа с файлами)\n","1. Использовать smolagents (или langgraph), чтобы создать агента с доступам к иструментам\n","1. Реализовать логику агента, который разбивает сложный запрос пользователя на отдельные шаги (например, “Найди блог про нанотехнологии, сделай саммари последней статьи, посчитай, сколько в ней слов”) и последовательно выполняет их\n","1. Протестировать агента на нескольких многошаговых запросах\n","\n","**Библиотеки:** smolagents (или langchain.agents, langgraph), requests (для запросов к веб-сервисам), duckduckgo-search (google search api или любая другая api для разработки инструмента)\n","\n","**Ожидаемый результат:** Colab-ноутбук с примером работы агента с доступом к внешним инструментам и multi-step reasoning (способность выполнять задачи из нескольких шагов)"],"metadata":{"id":"wqWhjavKihbM"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##  Подобрать набор инструментов"],"metadata":{"id":"mypLj9iMpsbb"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["Например, если задача выполнять запросы типа \"Найди блог про нанотехнологии, сделай саммари последней статьи, посчитай, сколько в ней слов\", то нам необходимы инструменты:\n","\n","\n","\n","*   Поиска\n","*   Исследования веб-страниц\n","*   Суммаризации\n","*   Произведения подсчетов\n","\n"],"metadata":{"id":"ObEB0sMDrGqB"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### Инструменты smolagents"],"metadata":{"id":"6I01G6dCpzBn"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["!pip install smolagents[litellm] ddgs requests beautifulsoup4 groq markdownify requests -q"],"metadata":{"id":"TWYeF4xifCg9"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["**Built-in**"],"metadata":{"id":"aJtLIETdnKXp"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["**Вот примеры built-in инструментов smolagents**\n","\n","*    Information Retrieval: Search and retrieve information from the web and specific knowledge sources.\n","\n","          ApiWebSearchTool\n","\n","          DuckDuckGoSearchTool\n","\n","          GoogleSearchTool\n","\n","          WebSearchTool\n","\n","          WikipediaSearchTool\n","\n","*    Web Interaction: Fetch and process content from specific web pages.\n","\n","          VisitWebpageTool\n","\n","*    Code Execution: Dynamic execution of Python code for computational tasks.\n","\n","          PythonInterpreterTool\n","\n","*    User Interaction: Enable Human-in-the-Loop collaboration between agents and users.\n","\n","         UserInputTool: Collect input from users.\n","\n","*    Speech Processing: Convert audio to textual data.\n","\n","          SpeechToTextTool\n","\n","*    Workflow Control: Manage and direct the flow of agent operations.\n","\n","          FinalAnswerTool: Conclude agent workflow with final response."],"metadata":{"id":"JsXbrl_DhZTm"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["import os\n","from groq import Groq\n","from google.colab import userdata\n","\n","# получаем API ключ из переменной окружения\n","GROQ_API_KEY = userdata.get('GROQ_API_KEY')"],"metadata":{"id":"DyxUyVlKpVt7"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# --- попробуем применить DuckDuckGoSearchTool для поиска в интернете ---\n","\n","from smolagents import CodeAgent, LiteLLMModel, DuckDuckGoSearchTool\n","\n","# тестовый запрос\n","input_text = \"Выполни поиск по запросу 'блог про нанотехнологии'\"\n","\n","# создаем модель LiteLLM для работы с Groq\n","model = LiteLLMModel(\n","    model_id=\"groq/llama-3.1-8b-instant\",\n","    api_key=GROQ_API_KEY,\n","    temperature=0.7\n",")\n","\n","# создаем агента с веб-поиском\n","agent = CodeAgent(\n","    tools=[DuckDuckGoSearchTool()], # пока один\n","    model=model,\n","    max_steps=10, # \"Maximum number of steps the agent can take to solve the task\"\n","    verbosity_level=2 # \"Level of verbosity of the agent’s logs\"\n",")\n","\n","# запускаем агента\n","print(input_text)\n","print(\"-\" * 50)\n","\n","result = agent.run(input_text)"],"metadata":{"id":"1GVenHmIfhiX"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# --- здесь протестируем другие built-in инструменты: все, какими будет пользоваться наш агент ---\n","\n"],"metadata":{"id":"XVxRKkfGi1-p"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["**Кастомные инструменты**"],"metadata":{"id":"z3GA3XPunRNj"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["class smolagents.Tool\n","\n","\n","---\n","\n","\n","attributes:\n","\n","  **description (str)** — A short description of what your tool does, the inputs it expects and the output(s) it will return.\n","  \n","  `‘This is a tool that downloads a file from a url. It takes the url as input, and returns the text contained in the file’.`\n","\n","  **name (str)** — The name usually describes what the tool does.\n","\n","  **inputs (Dict[str, Dict[str, Union[str, type, bool]]])** — A dictionary with keys \"type\" and \"description\". It contains information that helps the Python interpreter make educated choices about the input.\n","\n","  **output_type (type)** — The type of the tool output. The types for both inputs and output_type should be Pydantic formats, they can be either of these: [\"string\", \"boolean\",\"integer\", \"number\", \"image\", \"audio\", \"array\", \"object\", \"any\", \"null\"].\n","\n","\n","---\n","\n","methods:\n","\n","  **forward** — The method which contains the inference code to be executed."],"metadata":{"id":"pye9DRaLncDO"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["from smolagents import Tool"],"metadata":{"id":"dzMJmnrCllPg"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# --- пример инструмента для посчета длины текста ---\n","\n","from smolagents import Tool\n","\n","class WordCountTool(Tool):\n","    name = \"word_count\"\n","    description = \"\"\"\n","    Подсчитывает количество слов и символов в тексте.\n","    Используй когда нужно узнать длину текста или статьи.\n","    \"\"\"\n","    inputs = {\n","        \"text\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"Текст для подсчёта\"}\n","    }\n","    output_type = \"string\"\n","\n","    def forward(self, text: str) -> str:\n","        words = len(text.split())\n","        chars = len(text)\n","        return f\"Слов: {words}\\nСимволов: {chars}\"\n","\n","word_count = WordCountTool()"],"metadata":{"id":"8uycxZEMk3bp"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# --- создадим хотя бы один свой ---\n","\n"],"metadata":{"id":"g_KpdGp3qCza"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### Инструменты langgraph"],"metadata":{"id":"Kh5x7nuGscSc"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["!pip install langchain-core langgraph langchain_groq langchain_community -q"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"8qkHrRotssel","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1772212149730,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":13256,"user":{"displayName":"Catherine Kovalenko","userId":"14729822926829973326"}},"outputId":"13fbe62b-a5d5-426e-d3b6-8887fb9d2224"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["\u001b[?25l   \u001b[90m━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\u001b[0m \u001b[32m0.0/2.5 MB\u001b[0m \u001b[31m?\u001b[0m eta \u001b[36m-:--:--\u001b[0m\r\u001b[2K   \u001b[91m━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\u001b[0m\u001b[91m╸\u001b[0m \u001b[32m2.5/2.5 MB\u001b[0m \u001b[31m82.9 MB/s\u001b[0m et